 of initial data which ensures\nconvergence even in such $H^s$ regardless of the ratio.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 6 Sep 2022 16:42:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 17 Sep 2022 15:23:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-20"}
