ained from stabilized finite\nelement method and good properties of PINNs are highlighted.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 7 Sep 2022 07:52:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 10 Sep 2022 17:18:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-13"}
